target: I'm sorry, earlier you said you were going to Ely, but now you're asking about stevenage. What is your destination, please?

I just can't leave until 14:30 <system> There is a 15:50 train that will arrive at 16:07. Does that sound good?<user> Does the train depart on Friday? Does it go to Stevenage? <system>
